casebody.data:
Carolyn HILL-LOMAX, Petitioner,
v.
David VITTETOE, et al. No. 19-7629. Supreme Court of the United States. April 20, 2020

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until May 11, 2020, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a).
